column11: Description

The bunny is crafted with soft wool. It has the rounded structure body and rounded head is attached. Rising from the head two elongated ears with pink inner section. On the face black needled eyes completed with pink needled nose.
The egg is a soft pastel color base with white zigzag line.
The eggs are crafted with the soft wool. It has variety of colorful design including flower, polka dots, chocolate drizzle.
The base is wet felted. It is crafted with soft wool. It has different color options.
It features a felted Easter egg in soft orange tones with a bright yellow chick face detail in the center. The chick has tiny black eyes and an orange beak, giving it a cute and cheerful expression.

a small felt boy figure dressed in a bright green outfit with a yellow head covering, holding a pink egg decorated with yellow polka dots. The ornament has a smiling face and a simple handcrafted look, with a natural hanging string attached at the top, making it perfect for adding a playful and festive touch to seasonal decorations.
Bunny showcase a rustic brown body with distinct white belly patch,contrasting with delicate pink inner ears. Its face is simple design as eyes closed and stitched "X' for mouth.

The easter bunny handcrafted with soft wool. Measuring 12cm tall,it features a classic bunny silhouette, complete with perky ears and a simple yet expressive embroidered face, including a cross-stitched nose and closed eyes. The bunny is dressed in a vibrant pink, felt sleeveless dress worn over a short-sleeved top of the same cheerful hue, adding a touch of whimsy and detail to its overall appeal.
adorable felt bunnies nestled snugly within vibrant orange felt carrots, complete with green felt tops and stitched detailing to mimic real carrots.

Bunny is predominantly a soft lavender hue, with contrasting pale pink details on the inner ears and a neatly tied, cozy scarf around its neck, a sweet and gentle character. The facial features are subtly indicated with simple, embroidered black lines forming closed eyes and a small, upturned mouth, conveying a peaceful expression, further enhancing their endearing quality.

Crafted from soft, pure wool. It features a rounded body with prominently long, pointed ears lines with white felt. It is characterized by large,expressive black eyes with a teal outline, a simple black stitched nose, delicate black whiskers and two destinctive white buck teeth at the bottom.

Measuring 10.5cmin height, it features a grey felt bunny figure wearning a light blue felt jumpsuit, with white button details on the front. The bunny facial featues include stitched eyes and a pink nose, while its ears have contrasting pink inner lining.

Bunny is distinctly shaped to capture the iconic silhouette of a rabbit, complete with perky ears, a rounded body, and a delicate, fluffy tail, likely made from a pom-pom piece of felt in a complementary pastel shade. The faces are adorned with simple yet expressive hand-embroidered details, including small, dark eyes and potentially a nose, adding to their endearing and rustic appeal.

The cat is depicted wearing a cozy green sweater and carries a small, round brown Easter basket, adding a whimsical and festive touch. Its design emphasizes a cute and friendly aesthetic, with rounded features for the head, ears, and body, and delicate needle-felted details for the eyes, nose, and smiling mouth, creating an appealing expression that suggests a playful and gentle nature.

Pink felt Easter egg adorned with an array of bright yellow polka dots, adding a cheerful and playful touch. The egg also has an endearing, stylized sleepy face, characterized by gently arched, closed eyes and a subtle, content expression, which brings a whimsical and charming personality to the overall appearance.

The design is hand-felted yellow spring chick and a small, accompanying purple egg. The chick itself is crafted with a soft, rounded yellow body, featuring tiny black eyes, a small orange beak, and bright orange webbed feet. Spherical purple egg, also created with a needle-felting technique, presenting a slightly textured and uniform appearance.
It is crafted from the soft yellow wool. It featues a plump, round body , black eyes, and orange beak.

Crafted from a soft yet sturdy teal-colored felt, providing a delightful tactile experience and ensuring durability for holding treats and eggs. The basket features a vibrant green felt "grass" base, adding a touch of natural charm, and is adorned with appliqué details depicting two endearing white felt bunnies and small orange carrots, creating a whimsical Easter-themed scene.

The chick crafted from soft yellow roving wool has simple black bead eyes and a small orange felted beak conveying a sense of innocence and new life. The eggshell, split open to reveal the chick exhibiting a textured surface and a blend of colors to mimic a natural, speckled egg.
The design depicts a stylized woman wearing a simple brown coat, black shoes, and a distinctive white bonnet, with visible yellow hair peeking out. A miniature brown basket is clasped in hands.

It features pointy ears, needled whiskers, a little nose, and big embroidered blue eyes that give it a cute and playful personality. The basket has a rounded body with an open circular cut-out in the front for holding items and a handle on top for easy carrying.
